      • getOneEntityToSave

        <T extends com.bullhornsdk.data.model.entity.core.type.UpdateEntity> T getOneEntityToSave(T entity)
        Returns a deep copy of the passed in entity, if a entity of type T already exists in allEntitiesToSaveBackToBH that entity will be returned, otherwise this method will return a deep copy the entity passed in to the method. If the entity did not exist in the allDtosToSaveBackToBH map the returned copy will be added to the map.
        Parameters:
        entity - entity to be copied, if this object already exists in the allDtosToSaveBackToBH map then that entity will be returned.
        Returns:
        A deep copy of the passed in T entity.
